summary: This mod introduces a small Faerie into your game. She is a mistress of Atronach conjuration and powerful destruction magic. Lunariana can be found in a small nesting area within Eldergleam Sanctuary. Just follow the path to the Eldergleam tree and you will find her.  Note: This mod replaces any previous versions of Lunariana.
